# Architecture Review — Role Flow & Reusability

## Executive Summary

The system has **50 admin APIs**, **15 student APIs**, **8 teacher APIs**, and **13 public APIs**. The client is right — features were built independently without a unifying architecture. Here's the detailed map.

---

