| Feature | Admin | Teacher | Student | Public | Status |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Dashboard** | ✅ stats | ✅ classes/marks | ✅ profile summary | — | ✅ OK |
| **Courses/Programs** | ✅ CRUD | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ browse | ✅ OK |
| **Fees (StudentFee)** | ✅ assign/collect | ❌ | ✅ view own | — | ✅ Fixed |
| **Finance (FeePayment)** | ✅ dashboard/CRUD | ❌ | ❌ dead endpoint | — | 🟠 See #1 |
| **Attendance** | ✅ overview | ✅ mark/view | ❌ can't see own | — | 🔴 See #2 |
